Comment: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:33.61,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:213615,213615}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215159,216368}Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216368,218537}No matter the result\Nof your duel with Victor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218537,221832}I cannot approve of you\Nbeing my daughter's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222499,226628}The Rostain family\Nis a family of a high social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227045,230632}You have left a stain\Non our family's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231175,234219}But Mr. Jules risked his life\Nfor my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234219,235888}Silence, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235888,237890}This is adults talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237890,239016}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239016,240475}It's fine, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241185,244396}Father, I want to live\Ntogether with Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244396,246273}I am ready for consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246273,247566}– You stupid girl!\N– Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249276,250861}You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250861,252654}You're terrible, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262873,264416}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264416,267711}Geneviève.\NI will no longer attempt to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267711,271381}From now on, you are\Nno longer a part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272799,274718}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274718,275802}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276178,277971}Do not call me your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284394,287064}Marie. Don't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287064,289274}The Geneviève we knew is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289274,293028}Our only children are now\NAndréa and Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294571,297699}Master, the preparations\Nfor the departure are all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298742,300369}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300369,303330}All right. It is time, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309753,312881}Everyone go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318428,323976}{\i1}Did I raise her wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326603,328272}{\i1}Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330565,332818}{\i1}You were such a kind child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450977,452813}Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452813,454648}Everyone is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458318,459444}Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459444,460320}Yes, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460320,461738}There is something\NI would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461738,464658}I would like to release you\Nfrom serving our family as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464658,468078}Yes, Master.\NI can't say I didn't see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471581,473417}Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473417,474960}What is inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474960,479673}I have one more favor to ask.\NPlease watch over Geneviève for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479673,483760}Very difficult times are coming.\NUse this money to support her in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483760,485345}I know I am asking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486179,488640}Can you grant my wish\Nnonetheless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488640,490684}Yes, Master.\NI shall grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491852,493645}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494271,500110}To begin with, I was devoted\Nto Ms. Geneviève the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524634,526928}Andréa, I'm leaving\Nthe rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527220,528972}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528972,530307}Don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531975,533268}Andréa…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534478,536605}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536605,538732}I am not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538732,540609}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540609,542402}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542402,544738}All right, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551703,552537}Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567135,568011}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574351,575393}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575393,576311}Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577854,579689}{\i1}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585028,589032}Listen, Geneviève. This is the path\Nyou've chosen for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589032,591785}Do not look away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591785,594871}You can't take back\Nwhat you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617644,621856}{\i1}Later this afternoon,\NJules and Geneviève
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621856,627195}{\i1}had a low-key wedding ceremony\Nat a small church in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627571,632033}In the name of the Lord Almighty,\NI now pronounce you husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632576,633785}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651219,653888}Jules, I won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653888,655015}Take care of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655849,657809}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657809,659227}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659561,661688}You got what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661688,663273}Cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663565,665859}Thank you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666026,667736}Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667736,669404}There's one thing\NI fail to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669404,670363}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670363,672532}I mean your lovely bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672532,675201}Even though she just lost it all:\Nthe land, the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675201,677287}she looks so happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679748,681124}That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681875,683460}Andréa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684919,685962}Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691426,693136}I've been looking\Nfor you, Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703146,705940}I am sorry to disturb the harmony\Nof this occasion, but it is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705940,708401}The Prussian army\Nhas started surrounding Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708401,709861}What? So fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709861,712030}Damn it!\NVictor, give me your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712197,713490}Hm? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713490,716242}My family is on their way\Nto Versailles right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716242,718203}They might come across\Nthe enemy troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718370,720080}I understand.\NI will go warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720246,723416}No, it is too dangerous.\NI will take care of my family by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723416,725168}Give me your horse. Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727170,729005}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736346,737263}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740016,742435}You are beyond belief.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:39.78,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:759786,759786}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792944,798658}{\i1}The Prussian army started\Nto encircle the city of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798658,801870}{\i1}As the Rostain family\Nwas heading to Versailles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801870,805123}{\i1}many of the Prussian troops were\Nalready in the area, waiting for refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805540,807417}{\i1}However, the Rostains\Ndid not know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812964,815717}Hi! It's me, Jean,\Nwith my daily marriage proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815717,817469}Homesick already, Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818344,820764}Geez, stop following me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820764,822807}The sight of your face\Nmakes me nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823099,825059}Come on, before long,\Nyou'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825059,827937}And once you do, it's in the bag.\NI can already hear the church bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827937,829981}Tin-tan-din-dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829981,832901}My taste is not nearly bad enough\Nto get used to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832901,835945}Oh, I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835945,841451}You see, from now on, I'll follow you\Nwherever you go, like a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841743,843745}Oh, is that right?\NLike a shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843745,848875}Shadows do not blabber as much\Nand do not keep sending unwanted flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848875,850126}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850126,852545}Another rejection today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852545,854047}Today and tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854047,858176}Oh, whatever. If I hold out long enough,\Nyou'll grow to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858176,859052}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859052,860220}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860887,861971}I can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870688,872649}What was that?\NWhat is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873107,877779}Master, it seems we have entered\Nright into middle of a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877779,879072}What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879072,880406}Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885078,888248}We will cross that bridge,\Nthen we will go into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888248,889499}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929455,930832}Mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930832,931791}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931791,933543}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951436,954397}We should be\Nat a safe distance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955356,956608}Where is Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956608,958234}I can't see\Nher carriage anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958443,959569}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966784,968828}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969078,970872}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971289,972957}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973207,974667}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975043,977295}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979464,980798}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981424,982759}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982842,983801}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984135,985553}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986846,990016}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993895,995605}Victor! Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996272,997357}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999651,1001319}Isabelle…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004739,1006616}Isabelle, hang on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009827,1010787}Are you okay, Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010787,1011955}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012163,1014415}Geez, Victor again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014415,1016542}Why is he always interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016542,1021297}Hey, buddy!\NWe must have a little chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022799,1025677}On second thought,\Nwe can do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054956,1057166}Not good.\NThey blew up the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081399,1083359}What about the rest\Nof the Rostains?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083359,1086529}Well, they did cross the bridge.\NI think they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086529,1088489}They're probably\Nin Versailles by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090450,1093077}Thank goodness.\NWhat are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093786,1095955}The road to Versailles\Nis swarming with enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095955,1098166}Going back to Paris\Nseems to be our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098166,1100209}The way home\Nis full of enemies, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100209,1104047}If we go on foot,\Nwe'll get caught sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104505,1106049}It'll be fine, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106049,1107383}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129280,1130907}– What was that?\N– Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142335,1143503}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148132,1148966}There's a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155932,1157433}There's a cart.\NWe'll snatch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161729,1162897}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171155,1172198}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178329,1181040}Damn! Take this, you oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185419,1186337}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189173,1192009}Damn! Don't think you can mock me\Njust because you're big!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200184,1201102}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201811,1204021}Now you've done it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215074,1216868}You're so pathetic, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216868,1219996}You can't do\N{\i1}anything{\i0} without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220872,1222874}I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223499,1224959}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226252,1228296}Hands up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231340,1232675}Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232675,1234844}Jean, you take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235386,1237221}All right, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241934,1242977}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254697,1256240}After them!\NDon't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268878,1270213}Isabelle, can you drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271172,1272089}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272548,1274008}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277553,1279805}You can't shoot\Nrandomly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279805,1283142}Lean slightly forward.\NLet your body absorb the recoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293527,1296322}You don't need to aim at people.\NHorses are enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296906,1298199}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304622,1307291}Mr. Victor,\Nyour wound from the duel…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308376,1311212}Now's not the time for that.\NShoot. Keep shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316717,1317551}You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321472,1322473}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322723,1325184}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354880,1356173}It's our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356173,1357341}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367226,1372523}{\i1}The moment Isabelle had realized\Nthey were safe, she fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374358,1375526}{\i1}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382533,1384243}You saved our skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385661,1387121}Are you okay, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387830,1389999}Yes. All thanks to little Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392376,1395963}Let's get her to a carriage\Nsuitable for a lady like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398632,1400259}Such a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400259,1402261}You're still just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407933,1410353}Ah, there he goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1410353,1412688}Why does Victor\Nalways look so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417735,1422281}{\i1}Even though she was carried\Nby the person she longed for…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1423115,1427161}{\i1}Isabelle remained unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:57.08,Credits,[credits],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432124,1437088}{\fad(200,50)\c&HFAFAFA&\blur0.7\fs17\an5\pos(511,362)}To be continued
Comment: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:57.42,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1437421,1437421}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:24:00.38,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1437421,1440383}{\pos(298,458)}Next episode preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441425,1445388}General Gambetta heads to Versailles\Nin a hot-air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1445388,1448182}Thanks to my brother's position,\NI get to fly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448516,1452728}Ah! Soon I'll be able\Nto meet Mother and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452728,1454688}Mr. Victor is flying with us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454688,1456732}And so is Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1456732,1458192}The danger lurks everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1458192,1461237}I wonder if we can get\Nto Versailles safely?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1461237,1463656}Next time on "Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463656,1467368}"Escape in a Hot-air Balloon".\NPlease look forward to it.
Comment: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:27.32,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1467326,1467326}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:53.43,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1487429,1493435}{\blur0.5}anata no egao wa\Ntotemo suteki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:58.64,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493435,1498649}{\blur0.5}soyokaze no you ni\Natatakai ai ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:03.57,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498649,1503571}{\blur0.5}RANRARA hazunda uta wa\Nogawa wo koete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.57,0:25:08.74,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503571,1508742}{\blur0.5}midori no yama ni\Nkodama suru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.74,0:25:14.08,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508742,1514081}{\blur0.5}hora omoikiri\Nkakete yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.08,0:25:20.50,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1514081,1520504}{\blur0.5}ano hito no iru\Noka no ue made
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:53.43,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1487429,1493435}Your smile is so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:58.64,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493435,1498649}It displays so much love,\Ngentle like a breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:03.57,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498649,1503571}La la la, our song\Nreaches across the stream
